    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Upstanding collars originally derived from Chinese costume that do not roll over. Structurally, these are essentially bare collar stands with no fall. Shapes and method of attachment may vary.</Note_Text>
